name: De Matia
description: De Matia — As he grows stronger in human lust, De Matia trawls for greed and cruelty in human deeds. It's also possible to view them as corpse eaters. The scent of their enemies will cause him to turn into the most terrifying beast. From the unpleasant and  horrifying scents, you will know that De Matia is nearby. Ready to hunt its’ prey.
